zey hobn z- gehaltn ordenung. m'hot ge- ah tsugeshtelt tsu di arbet, tseyln.

572
00:28:19,729 --> 00:28:21,970
zey zenen nisht gevezn keyn spetsyele

573
00:28:21,970 --> 00:28:23,959
me z- me ken onrufn kapos.

574
00:28:24,302 --> 00:28:27,603
zey hobn geholfn ⟨az in la-⟩ emetser hot gemuzt haltn ordenung in lager.

575
00:28:27,694 --> 00:28:29,564
iz emetser hot dokh gemuzt

576
00:28:29,564 --> 00:28:31,370
zey hobn gedenkt az mit dem

577
00:28:31,370 --> 00:28:33,341
tsufelik hobn zey ale dray ibergelebt.

578
00:28:33,448 --> 00:28:36,069
ober zene- tsvey zenen ⟨shoyn⟩ geshtorbn. eyner

579
00:28:36,069 --> 00:28:39,112
yednfals, ⟨hobn nokh⟩ gezen mit tsvey yor UNK gezen.

580
00:28:40,992 --> 00:28:43,449
vos nokh gedenkt ir fun Tshenstokhov?

581
00:28:43,405 --> 00:28:48,562
fun Tshenstokhov, keyn faln fun d- fun shisn iz in Tshenstokhov nisht gevezn.

582
00:28:50,762 --> 00:28:53,641
s- in Tshenstokhov zenen nokh gevezn dray opteylungen.

583
00:28:54,036 --> 00:28:55,037
s'iz gevezn

584
00:28:55,037 --> 00:28:56,966
WARTA, dos ikh hob gearbet.

585
00:28:57,192 --> 00:28:58,859
s'iz gevezn PELCERY

586
00:28:58,859 --> 00:29:00,391
vos mayn froy hot gearbet

587
00:29:00,904 --> 00:29:02,369
kh'hob dokh demolt zi nisht gekent.

588
00:29:02,369 --> 00:29:03,902
un s'iz gevezn RAKOW.

589
00:29:04,802 --> 00:29:09,296
dray, ale dray hobn gearbet, UNK geven farshidene opteylungen fun farshidene amunitsye.

590
00:29:09,296 --> 00:29:13,604
eynem, eynem hot men gemakht di laykhte arbet, laykhte ⟨koyln⟩, dos iz geven bay undz

591
00:29:14,202 --> 00:29:14,972
un

592
00:29:15,383 --> 00:29:18,617
bay di PELCERY ⟨hot men⟩ oykh gemakht ⟨koyln⟩.

593
00:29:18,943 --> 00:29:21,451
in RAKOW hot men gemakht shvere bombes.

594
00:29:23,061 --> 00:29:24,036
un

595
00:29:24,036 --> 00:29:26,196
un dos iz anfang

596
00:29:26,196 --> 00:29:30,649
g- azoy i- meyn veynikster iz gevezn normal di lage, keyn

597
00:29:31,009 --> 00:29:35,590
zenen, mentshn zenen gefaln nebekh fun, fun hunger, ober nisht fun vos m'hot geshosn mamesh.

598
00:29:35,683 --> 00:29:40,706
dort zent ir oykh geven bavakht bay daytshn oder l- oykh andere?

599
00:29:40,172 --> 00:29:41,634
daytshn un ukrainer.

